  "body": "<p>If you read this blog mainly for scrapbooking posts, then chances are you've already heard the sad news that after 15 years, Two Peas in a Bucket is closing.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/90ba2a5494d7b1ea.png?v=1782529640\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I started scrapbooking in 2007 mainly as a therapeutic creative outlet. Two Peas was one of the first places I learned all about products, what the initials DD, DH, and DT stood for (dear daughter, dear husband and design team). It's one of the first places online that I sought out inspiration. A couple years ago when I was a garden girl, I visited the headquarters. While I could go on and on about how deeply saddened I am about this institution closing, I will focus on what an amazing resource it was for the memory keeping community. I am endlessly grateful to the founders for all they have done for the scrapbooking and paper crafting industry.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/50d40a15023838a4.jpg?v=1782529643\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>On a happier note, a week from today, my online workshop with Kelly Purkey - <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=52016&amp;m=9622&amp;afftrack=here%26there&amp;urllink=www%2Ebigpictureclasses%2Ecom%2Fhere%2Dand%2Dthere%2Ephp\">Here &amp; There Inspiration</a> begins!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n<iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/Z966hl7bJaM?list=UUE12qx0-jGjEzYIGeK6_ZAg\"></iframe>\n\n\n\n\n<p>We've put together awesome PDF's, bonus tips, how-to's and over 20 videos that you'll have forever access to, so don't worry if your summer plans are already booked. Hope you'll join us for </p><p><a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=52016&amp;m=9622&amp;afftrack=here%26there&amp;urllink=www%2Ebigpictureclasses%2Ecom%2Fhere%2Dand%2Dthere%2Ephp\">Here &amp; There Inspiration</a></p>"
}